["<div dir=\"rtl\" align=\"right\">\n\n\n <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: -52.65pt\" dir=\"rtl\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   لَا تَجْزَعَنَّ مِنَ الْهِزَالِ فَإِنَّمَا</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   ذُبِحَ السَّمِينُ وَ عُوفِيَ الْمَهْزُولُ‏</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">وَ \n اجْعَلْ فُؤَادَكَ لِلتَّوَاضُعِ مَنْزِلًا</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">إِنَّ \n التَّوَاضُعَ بِالشَّرِيفِ جَمِيلٌ‏</td>\n  </tr>\n   <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">وَ \n إِذَا وَلِيتَ أُمُورَ قَوْمٍ لَيْلَةً</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;فَاعْلَمْ \n بِأَنَّكَ عَنْهُمُ مَسْئُولٌ‏</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">وَ \n إِذَا حَمَلْتَ إِلَى الْقُبُورِ جَنَازَةً </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n فَاعْلَمْ بِأَنَّكَ بَعْدَهَا مَحْمُولٌ‏</td>\n  </tr>\n   <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">يَا \n صَاحِبَ الْقَبْرِ الُمَنَقَّشِ سَطْحُهُ</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">وَ \n لَعَلَّهُ مِنْ تَحْتِهِ مَغْلُولٌ‏</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">مَا \n يَنْفَعَنْهُ أَنْ يَكُونَ مُنَقَّشاً </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">وَ \n عَلَيْهِ مِنْ حَلَقِ الْعَذَابِ كُبُولٌ‏</td>\n  </tr>\n   <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">لَا \n تَغْتَرِرْ بِنَعِيمِهِمْ وَ بِمُلْكِهِمْ</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n الْمُلْكُ يَفْنَى وَ النَّعِيمُ يَزُول</td>\n  </tr>\n    </table>\n  \n</div>\n\n","ديوان الإمام علي(ع)"]